 motifs has been found preserved in ice in Siberia. It is now on display at the Hermitage Museum\/ St. Petersburg, Russia.<br \/>\nBactrian\/Parthian is led by a Median usher. The Parthian wears a headband and a belt over a tunic with trousers tucked in boots. He\u2019s carrying a metal drinking bowl of wine. There\u2019s been a 20 cm golden bowl found in Iran and on display at the Iran National museum. Other images show Bactrians carrying beakers and a two-humped camel.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Location: Persepolis, Apadana Palace, eastern portico, southern staircase. Babylonian delegation ushered by a Median noble [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":328,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/383"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=383"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/383\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":545,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/383\/revisions\/545"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/328"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=383"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMind.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=383"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.OpenEyesOpenMin